{"tid":2224630,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"又傷了！皇馬宣佈攻擊王牌肌肉受傷 恐缺戰一個月","createTime":"2020-09-30T15:56:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-02T04:39:19.000Z","uid":34571,"like":32,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"13277dff84362b8b2f157143957c5e6fc2fd475d","tid":2224630,"uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T15:56:46.000Z","msg":"香港時間9月30日晚上，皇馬在其官網宣佈，球隊大將夏薩特右腿肌肉受傷。有皇馬跟隊記者稱，夏薩特需要傷缺3到4周時間。<br />\n<br />\n  夏薩特去年夏天，以1億歐元的轉會費加盟皇馬。但受傷病影響，他上季只為皇馬出場了22次，攻入1球。今季截至目前，他還未有過出場。<br />\n<br />\n  加盟皇馬之後，夏薩特上季受傷了4次，如今這次受傷，是他轉投皇馬後的第5次受傷。"},{"pid":"9963fa016189de7d402d73af73599d477df83afe","tid":2224630,"uid":36906,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T15:58:54.000Z","msg":"坐係到收$ 不知幾爽"},{"pid":"73cf400593d52f874a7a9849c86bdf2c86f515df","tid":2224630,"uid":59283,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T16:01:40.000Z","msg":"繼續食漢堡包<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c6e66359508507fbea47ee2f33d35e605d2fe68","tid":2224630,"uid":120965,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T16:06:03.000Z","msg":"世三<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9fe2ae61022b5e14d62e150373fc4a4d54c5440","tid":2224630,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T16:34:21.000Z","msg":"以為講賓周"},{"pid":"e9f859b70322d8d049fd6f787049a2c9ce7adf6f","tid":2224630,"uid":20611,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"b9fe2ae61022b5e14d62e150373fc4a4d54c5440","tid":2224630,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T16:34:21.000Z","msg":"以為講賓周"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T16:39:53.000Z","msg":"一講王牌淨係諗起賓周"},{"pid":"b1007e87bd86d4a73a84eecbfd680915459d8064","tid":2224630,"uid":365100,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0